comment: Lillard (POR) maintains a legal guarding position as he defends Morris' (WAS) shot attempt.
Lillard (POR) and Morris (WAS) briefly engage and separate after the defensive switch and during rebounding.
Morris (WAS) makes incidental contact with Lillard (POR) that does not affect his RSBQ.
Dudley (WAS) sets the screen on Davis (POR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
RATR shows that Gortat (WAS) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Lillard (POR) that affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was last touched by Davis (POR) prior to going OOB was confirmed.
LHH shows that Lillard (POR) cleanly strips the ball prior to any incidental contact with Morris' (WAS) arm.
Plumlee (POR) jumps from point A to point B and makes body to body contact with Morris (WAS).
Henderson (POR) does not inbound the ball within 5 seconds.
Temple (WAS) makes incidental contact with McCollum (POR) that does not affect his RSBQ. Temple then trips over his own foot causing him to fall to the ground.
Henderson (POR) and Plumlee (POR) maintain legal guarding position and cleanly block Gortat's (WAS) layup attempt.
Leonard (POR) sets the screen on Sessions (WAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Morris (WAS) is correctly called for the delay of game.
Morris (WAS) lowers his shoulder into Lillard (POR), who obtains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact.
Henderson (POR) obtains a legal guarding position and jumps vertically as he contests Dudley's (WAS) driving shot attempt.
Leonard (POR) sets the screen on Sessions (WAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Wall (WAS) walks under the airborne shooter Lillard (POR) and makes contact with him on his jump shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Lillard (POR) was behind the three point line on his FG attempt at the 3:26 mark of the OT period was confirmed.
RHH shows that Wall (WAS) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Lillard's (POR) drive to the basket and layup attempt.
Gortat (WAS) sets the screen on Henderson (POR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Dudley (WAS) commits a take foul on Davis (POR).
Wall (WAS) commits a take foul on Leonard (POR).
Gortat (WAS) firms up as he sets the screen on Henderson (POR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Gortat (WAS) commits a take foul on Lillard (POR).
